Welcome to Kings Cross Surgery.

We have a friendly group of both Male and Female doctors. 

**Register as a patient at this practice**: www.camdengp.co.uk/new-patients/

 

We also offer Online GP Services for registered patients, so you can:

  • Book and cancel Appointments
  • View your Medical Records
  • Renew your Prescriptions
  • Message My GP

If you are a registered patient, Sign up for Online Services now: www.camdengp.co.uk/online-services

Dorking Medical Practice is comprised of New House Surgery in the town centre, Hillside Surgery on top of Box Hill and Riverbank Surgery in the village of Westcott.  

The 4 partners and 8 salaried GPs plus a team of Practice Nurses, HCAs and a Phlebotomist look after 11,300 patients in the area with the help of our First Contact Physiotherapists, First Contact Psychological Practitioners, Social Prescribers, Clinical Pharmacists, Paramedic Practitioner, Specialist Respiratory and Diabetes Nurses plus the reception/administration team.  

We offer various services including baby clinics, minor operations, respiratory clinics, diabetes clinics, heart disease clinics, well woman clinics, microsuction clinics and many more.

**NOW OPEN MONDAY TO FRIDAY 8AM - 8PM!**

Welcome to Richmond Road Medical Centre!

We are a forward thinking, innovative practice based in Hackney and we strive to offer an accessible, efficient and high-quality service for our patients.

‘Winner of GP Team of the Year 2020’ at the highly regarded National General Practice Awards 2020

** WINNER - Highly Commended for 'GP of the Year 2018 (England) **

We are extremely excited to announce that our very own Dr Gopal Mehta (GP Partner) has been named as one of the top doctors in the country! 

Dr Mehta was highly commended in the GP of the Year Category at the General Practice Awards which were held on the 30th November 2018.

Congratulations from the entire team here at Richmond Road!

**WINNERS - General Practice Team of the Year 2017 (England) ** 

We are extremely proud to announce that Richmond Road Medical Centre have been announced as **WINNERS** for the Prestigious National GP Awards 2017 as General Practice Team of the Year 2017.

Richmond Road Medical Centre has become the first practice in Hackney to win a National GP Award. 

The surgery was one of only five others on the shortlist, following hundreds of nominations across England.

The award celebrates the team that had the largest positive impact on improving patient care in their GP practice and their local area.

For more information on the awards please visit: http://www.generalpracticeawards.com

 

**NEW PATIENTS - SAME DAY REMOTE Registration Service**

We are now offering a same day registration service - Simply complete the online registration form via our website, and then call us on 0207 254 2298 to complete your registration. 

All our newly registered patients get a:

GP Telephone Consultation within 24 hours

GP Appointment within 48 hours

 

**48 HOUR ACCESS FOR ALL PATIENTS** 

 All of our registered patients get seen within 48 hours of making contact with the surgery.

Welcome to Balaam Street Surgery, providing primary care for Plaistow and surrounding areas. We hope you take your time to browse our website where you will find lots of useful information about the surgery and the services we offer.

Balaam Street Surgery provides SAME DAY CARE. This means that if you have a clinical problem we try to help you with that problem the same day, typically within a few hours of your request.

To help us provide you same day care please click here. The first time you use this service you will be asked to register. Then you will be asked to answer some quick questions and submit your form. Your request will be reviewed by a clinician who will telephone you within 2 hours, and often much quicker.

For a more detailed explanation please see our website.

Please click here to get same day care.

If you have any questions or suggestions, please contact the individual practice which you have in mind.

Our friendly local practice offers a wide range of dental services and our clinicians have a wealth of experience enabling them to provide advice and treatment on all aspects of dental care from General Dentistry to Hygienist Services, Cosmetic Dentistry, Dental Implants and Teeth Whitening

Over four million people in the UK trust mydentist with their dental care and we remain committed to providing the latest treatments and helping the nation to continue to improve their oral health.

We look forward to seeing you in practice

value.SummaryText:
Park House Care Home is a high-quality nursing home for people with advanced Dementia and is located in Kinlet, near the charming riverside town of Bewdley. The pleasant location is convenient for families and friends; with its close transport links to Kidderminster and Bridgnorth. With over 3 acres of magnificent gardens and a highly professional care team, Park House Care Home provides expert care and support in a splendid environment.

Highly trained and experienced care team provide specialist dementia care for people with complex needs in a calm and caring environment. The home offers advanced dementia care as well as specialist care for those with life-limiting conditions.

Park House Care Home naturally develop and maintain very detailed person-centred care plans that ensure that each resident receives first-rate care and support that is tailored to their specific needs. However, the key to Park House’s phenomenal reputation is the way their hugely experienced care team work with resident’s and their families to identify how to provide very individual care and maximise the quality of life even for residents who may previously have come from care homes unable to meet their complex needs.

The expert care team are committed to providing exceptional standards of care and a ‘home from home’ environment that is adapted to the resident’s needs whilst being welcoming and comfortable for both residents and their families. There are no set visiting times and friends and family are able to stay overnight. The home also offers free dining for friends and family and hold regular family events and activity days.
